trans-unit.source: Receives status information about a build from the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Tar emot statusinformation om en version från den <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: A ClientBuildManagerCallback object can be passed to the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager> object through the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.PrecompileApplication%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Ett ClientBuildManagerCallback-objekt kan skickas till den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>objekt via den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.PrecompileApplication%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.PrecompileApplication%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>

trans-unit.source: When an error is encountered during an application build, the error is passed as an argument to either the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportCompilerError%2A> or the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportParseError%2A> method, depending on the type of error.
trans-unit.target: När ett fel upptäcks under en program-konstruktion felet skickas som ett argument till antingen den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportCompilerError%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportParseError%2A>metod, beroende på vilken typ av fel.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportParseError%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback.ReportCompilerError%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you create a class that derives from the ClientBuildManagerCallback class, you can implement these methods and retrieve the error.
trans-unit.target: Du kan implementera dessa metoder och hämta felet när du skapar en klass som härleds från klassen ClientBuildManagerCallback.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerCallback"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Returns a lifetime service object that can be used to control the lifetime policy for this instance.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en livslängd service-objekt som kan användas till att styra livstid principen för den här instansen.

trans-unit.source: Reports compilation errors and warnings that occur during an application build.
trans-unit.target: Rapporter kompileringsfel och varningar som kan uppstå under en version av programmet.

trans-unit.source: The error or warning encountered during compilation.
trans-unit.target: Felet eller varningen uppstod under kompilering.

trans-unit.source: Reports parsing errors and warnings that occur during an application build.
trans-unit.target: Rapporter om fel och varningar som kan uppstå under en program-build-parsning.

trans-unit.source: The error or warning encountered during parsing.
trans-unit.target: Felet eller varningen uppstod vid parsning.

trans-unit.source: Reports the progress of an application build.
trans-unit.target: Rapporterar förlopp för en version av programmet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the current status of the build.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som innehåller den aktuella statusen för versionen.</xref:System.String>
